				August 22, 2015 at 22:31					</a>
									</div><!-- .comment-meta .commentmetadata -->

				<div class="comment-body"><p>No, we are saying that slate-voting should be banned.    Legitimate votes will always be drowned out by slate voting, because legitimate voters will be dispersed amongst as wide number of choices (that is, they will vote for what they actually enjoy) so that a small number of slate-voters concentrating on the proposed slate will almost always outnumber them.  </p>
<p>If slate-voting is tolerated, the Hugos will die. Period.</p>
</div>

